main event: A witness reported seeing a bright circular object resembling a silver sphere flying very low and fast over a residential area in Chicago.
interesting points: The object was observed by one individual,The sighting lasted for approximately 10 minutes,The object was reported to be traveling at speed and in a level course,The report included insufficient data for a conclusive evaluation,The sighting was part of Project Blue Book's investigation.
